{"id":244,"ayahs":[{"number":70,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا جَهَّزَهُم بِجَهَازِهِمْ جَعَلَ ٱلسِّقَايَةَ فِى رَحْلِ أَخِيهِ ثُمَّ أَذَّنَ مُؤَذِّنٌ أَيَّتُهَا ٱلْعِيرُ إِنَّكُمْ لَسَٰرِقُونَ","translation":"And [later,] when he had provided them with their provisions, he placed the [King's] drinking-cup in his brother's camel-pack. And [as they were leaving the city,] a herald called out: \"O you people of the caravan! Verily, you are thieves!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1666.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":59553,"position":1,"arabic":"فَلَمَّا","translation":"অতঃপর যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59554,"position":2,"arabic":"جَهَّزَهُم","translation":"তাদেরকে সে প্রস্তুত করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59555,"position":3,"arabic":"بِجَهَازِهِمْ","translation":"সহ তাদের খাদ্য সামগ্রী","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59556,"position":4,"arabic":"جَعَلَ","translation":"সে রেখে দিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59557,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلسِّقَايَةَ","translation":"(নিজের) পানপাত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59558,"position":6,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59559,"position":7,"arabic":"رَحْلِ","translation":"মালপত্রের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59560,"position":8,"arabic":"أَخِيهِ","translation":"তার ভাইয়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59561,"position":9,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59562,"position":10,"arabic":"أَذَّنَ","translation":"ঘোষণা দিলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59563,"position":11,"arabic":"مُؤَذِّنٌ","translation":"এক ঘোষক","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59564,"position":12,"arabic":"أَيَّتُهَا","translation":"\"হে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59565,"position":13,"arabic":"ٱلْعِيرُ","translation":"যাত্রীদল","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59566,"position":14,"arabic":"إِنَّكُمْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই তোমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59567,"position":15,"arabic":"لَسَـٰرِقُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই চোর\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_070_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":59568,"position":16,"arabic":"٧٠","translation":"(৭০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":71,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ وَأَقْبَلُوا۟ عَلَيْهِم مَّاذَا تَفْقِدُونَ","translation":"Turning towards the herald and his companions, the brothers asked: \"What is it that you miss?\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1667.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":60102,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_071_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60103,"position":2,"arabic":"وَأَقْبَلُوا۟","translation":"এবং এগিয়ে এলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_071_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60104,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَيْهِم","translation":"দিকে তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_071_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60105,"position":4,"arabic":"مَّاذَا","translation":"\"কি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_071_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60106,"position":5,"arabic":"تَفْقِدُونَ","translation":"তোমরা হারিয়েছো\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_071_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60107,"position":6,"arabic":"٧١","translation":"(৭১)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":72,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ نَفْقِدُ صُوَاعَ ٱلْمَلِكِ وَلِمَن جَآءَ بِهِۦ حِمْلُ بَعِيرٍۢ وَأَنَا۠ بِهِۦ زَعِيمٌۭ","translation":"They answered: \"We miss the King's goblet; and he who produces it shall receive a camel-load [of grain as reward]!\" And [the herald added:] \"I pledge myself to this _ [promise]!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1668.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":60522,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60523,"position":2,"arabic":"نَفْقِدُ","translation":"\"আমরা হারিয়েছি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60524,"position":3,"arabic":"صُوَاعَ","translation":"পানপাত্র","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60525,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلْمَلِكِ","translation":"রাজার","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60526,"position":5,"arabic":"وَلِمَن","translation":"এবং যে কেউ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60527,"position":6,"arabic":"جَآءَ","translation":"আসবে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60528,"position":7,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"নিয়ে তা (সে খাদ্য পাবে)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60529,"position":8,"arabic":"حِمْلُ","translation":"বোঝা পরিমাণ","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60530,"position":9,"arabic":"بَعِيرٍۢ","translation":"এক উটের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60531,"position":10,"arabic":"وَأَنَا۠","translation":"এবং আমি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60532,"position":11,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"এ সম্বন্ধে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60533,"position":12,"arabic":"زَعِيمٌۭ","translation":"মুখপাত্র\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_072_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":60534,"position":13,"arabic":"٧٢","translation":"(৭২)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":73,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ تَٱللَّهِ لَقَدْ عَلِمْتُم مَّا جِئْنَا لِنُفْسِدَ فِى ٱلْأَرْضِ وَمَا كُنَّا سَٰرِقِينَ","translation":"Said [the brothers]: \"By God! Well do you know that we have not come to commit deeds of corruption in this land, and that we have not been thieving!\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1669.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":61025,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61026,"position":2,"arabic":"تَٱللَّهِ","translation":"\"শপথ আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61027,"position":3,"arabic":"لَقَدْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61028,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلِمْتُم","translation":"তোমরা জেনেছো (যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61029,"position":5,"arabic":"مَّا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61030,"position":6,"arabic":"جِئْنَا","translation":"আমরা এসেছি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61031,"position":7,"arabic":"لِنُفْسِدَ","translation":"জন্যে আমরা খারাপ কাজ করার","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61032,"position":8,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61033,"position":9,"arabic":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","translation":"এ দেশের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61034,"position":10,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং নই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61035,"position":11,"arabic":"كُنَّا","translation":"আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61036,"position":12,"arabic":"سَـٰرِقِينَ","translation":"চোর\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_073_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61037,"position":13,"arabic":"٧٣","translation":"(৭৩)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":74,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ فَمَا جَزَٰٓؤُهُۥٓ إِن كُنتُمْ كَٰذِبِينَ","translation":"[The Egyptians] said: \"But what shall be the requital of this [deed] if you are [proved to be] liars?\"","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1670.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":61368,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_074_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61369,"position":2,"arabic":"فَمَا","translation":"\"তবে কি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_074_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61370,"position":3,"arabic":"جَزَٰٓؤُهُۥٓ","translation":"তার শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_074_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61371,"position":4,"arabic":"إِن","translation":"যদি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_074_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61372,"position":5,"arabic":"كُنتُمْ","translation":"তোমরা হও","audioUrl":"wbw/012_074_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61373,"position":6,"arabic":"كَـٰذِبِينَ","translation":"মিথ্যাবাদী\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_074_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61374,"position":7,"arabic":"٧٤","translation":"(৭৪)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":75,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟ جَزَٰٓؤُهُۥ مَن وُجِدَ فِى رَحْلِهِۦ فَهُوَ جَزَٰٓؤُهُۥ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ نَجْزِى ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"[The brothers] replied: \"Its requital? He in whose camel-pack [the cup] is found-he shall be [enslaved as] a requital thereof! Thus do we [ourselves] requite the doers of [such] wrong.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1671.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":61906,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالُوا۟","translation":"তারা বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61907,"position":2,"arabic":"جَزَٰٓؤُهُۥ","translation":"\"তার শাস্তি","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61908,"position":3,"arabic":"مَن","translation":"যার","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61909,"position":4,"arabic":"وُجِدَ","translation":"পাওয়া যাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61910,"position":5,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61911,"position":6,"arabic":"رَحْلِهِۦ","translation":"তার মালপত্রের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61912,"position":7,"arabic":"فَهُوَ","translation":"অতঃপর সেই","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61913,"position":8,"arabic":"جَزَٰٓؤُهُۥ ۚ","translation":"তার বিনিময় হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61915,"position":9,"arabic":"كَذَٰلِكَ","translation":"এভাবে","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61916,"position":10,"arabic":"نَجْزِى","translation":"প্রতিদান দিই আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61917,"position":11,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","translation":"সীমালঙ্ঘনকারীদেরকে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/012_075_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":61918,"position":12,"arabic":"٧٥","translation":"(৭৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":76,"arabic":"فَبَدَأَ بِأَوْعِيَتِهِمْ قَبْلَ وِعَآءِ أَخِيهِ ثُمَّ ٱسْتَخْرَجَهَا مِن وِعَآءِ أَخِيهِ ۚ كَذَٰلِكَ كِدْنَا لِيُوسُفَ ۖ مَا كَانَ لِيَأْخُذَ أَخَاهُ فِى دِينِ ٱلْمَلِكِ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ ۚ نَرْفَعُ دَرَجَٰتٍۢ مَّن نَّشَآءُ ۗ وَفَوْقَ كُلِّ ذِى عِلْمٍ عَلِيمٌۭ","translation":"Thereupon [they were brought before Joseph to be searched; and] he began with the bags of his half-brothers before the bag of his brother [Benjamin]: and in the end he brought forth the drinking Cups out of his brother's bag. In this way did We contrive for Joseph [the attainment of his heart's desire]: under the King's law, he would [otherwise] not have been able to detain his brother, had not God so willed. We do raise to [high] degrees [of knowledge] whomever We will - but above everyone who is endowed with knowledge there is One who knows all.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1672.mp3","surahId":12,"words":[{"id":62657,"position":1,"arabic":"فَبَدَأَ","translation":"অতঃপর (তল্লাশি) সে শুরু করলো","audioUrl":"wbw/012_076_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":62658,"position":2,"arabic":"بِأَوْعِيَتِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের পাত্রের","audioUrl":"wbw/012_076_002.mp3","charTypeNam